      <title>Philips Hue iOS SDK 사용하기</title>
      <link href="/2018/04/25/180425-philipshue/"/>
      <url>/2018/04/25/180425-philipshue/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>Philips Hue iOS SDK를 Xcode 프로젝트에 추가하기<br><a id="more"></a></p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image00.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="Prerequisites"><a href="#Prerequisites" class="headerlink" title="Prerequisites"></a>Prerequisites</h2><h3 id="Downloads"><a href="#Downloads" class="headerlink" title="Downloads"></a>Downloads</h3><ul><li>HueSDK from Philips Github: <a href="https://github.com/PhilipsHue/HueSDK" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HueSDK.framework</a><ul><li>해당 git를 ‘download or clone’하면 HueSDK를 얻을 수 있다.</li></ul></li><li>HueSDK iOS Framework Guide: <a href="https://github.com/PhilipsHue/HueSDK/blob/master/HueSDK/Apple/GettingStarted_Apple" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HueSDK iOS Framework Guide</a></li></ul><h3 id="env"><a href="#env" class="headerlink" title="env."></a>env.</h3><ul><li>Philips Hue Ambiance Starter Kit<ul><li>Hue Bridge</li><li>Hue 조명</li></ul></li><li>macOS 10.13 (High Sierra)<ul><li>Xcode 9</li><li>iOS 11.3</li><li>Swift4</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="Getting-Started"><a href="#Getting-Started" class="headerlink" title="Getting Started"></a>Getting Started</h2><h3 id="1-새-Xcode-프로젝트-만들기"><a href="#1-새-Xcode-프로젝트-만들기" class="headerlink" title="1. 새 Xcode 프로젝트 만들기"></a>1. 새 Xcode 프로젝트 만들기</h3><ul><li>Project Name: HueController</li><li>Template: Single View</li><li>Language: Swift</li></ul><h3 id="2-Framework-추가하기"><a href="#2-Framework-추가하기" class="headerlink" title="2. Framework 추가하기"></a>2. Framework 추가하기</h3><ol><li>Project Directory에 Dependencies 폴더 생성하고, HueSDK.framework 복사</li></ol><ul><li><p>~/home/HueController/Dependencies/<strong><a href="https://github.com/PhilipsHue/HueSDK" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HueSDK.framework</a></strong> (for device)</p></li><li><p>주의: <a href="https://github.com/PhilipsHue/HueSDK/blob/master/HueSDK/Apple/GettingStarted_Apple" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HueSDK iOS Framework Guide</a>를 보면 device, simulator의 Framework를 한번에 추가하는 방법으로 알려주는데, 빠른 실행과 결과를 보기 위해 device Framework만 추가한다.</p></li></ul><ol start="2"><li><p>Xcode에서 <strong>Dependencies</strong>그룹을 생성하고, 위에서 복사한 HueSDK.framework을 drag&amp;drop으로 Add Reference</p><div class="image-left"><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image03.png" alt=""></div></li><li><p>Target &gt; Build Phases &gt; <strong>Link Binary With Libraries</strong>에 Project Navigation에서 HueSDK.framework을 drag&amp;drop으로 추가</p><div class="image-left"><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image04.png" alt=""></div></li><li><p>Target &gt; General &gt; <strong>Embedded Binaries</strong>에 HueSDK.framework 추가</p><div class="image-left"><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image05.png" alt=""></div></li><li><p>Objective-C Briding Header추가를 위해 Header.h 추가</p></li></ol><ul><li><p>New File &gt; Header file</p><ul><li>File Name: <strong>Header.h</strong><div class="image-left"><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image06.png" alt=""></div></li></ul></li><li><p>Target &gt; Build Settings &gt; Objective-C Bridging Header 수정</p><div class="image-left"><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image08.png" alt=""></div></li><li><p>Header.h에 다음 내용 추가</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#import &lt;HueSDK/HueSDK.h&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="3-Enable-Bitcode"><a href="#3-Enable-Bitcode" class="headerlink" title="3. Enable Bitcode"></a>3. Enable Bitcode</h3><ul><li>No</li></ul><h3 id="4-Build-amp-Run"><a href="#4-Build-amp-Run" class="headerlink" title="4. Build &amp; Run"></a>4. Build &amp; Run</h3><ul><li>HueSDK.framework for device만 추가했기때문에,<br>빌드 전에 빌드대상을 Device 또는 Generic iOS Device를 선택한다.<div class="image-left"><img src="/images/180425-philipshue/image07.png" alt=""></div></li></ul><h2 id="Hue-SDK-Guide"><a href="#Hue-SDK-Guide" class="headerlink" title="Hue SDK Guide"></a>Hue SDK Guide</h2><p><a href="https://www.developers.meethue.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.developers.meethue.com/</a> 에 회원등록하면, 자세한 Hue SDK Guide를 확인할 수 있다.</p><h2 id="맛보기"><a href="#맛보기" class="headerlink" title="맛보기"></a>맛보기</h2><p>HueSDK가 잘 추가되었는지 확인하기 위해서 아래 코드를 삽입해서 Build &amp; Run 해본다.</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> documentsPath = <span class="type">NSSearchPathForDirectoriesInDomains</span>(.documentDirectory, .userDomainMask, <span class="literal">true</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>]        </span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">PHSPersistence</span>.setStorageLocation(documentsPath, andDeviceId: <span class="string">"001122334455"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">PHSLog</span>.setConsoleLogLevel(<span class="type">PHSLogLevel</span>.debug)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- # HUE API study## 뷸 켜기전에1. HUE브릿지 버튼 누르기2. 아래 URL로 POST눌러서 BODY 보내기<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: /api</span><br><span class="line">body: &#123;&quot;devicetype&quot;:&quot;my_hue_app#iphone peter&quot;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">method: POST</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li><h2 id="불-켜기-Turning-a-light-on"><a href="#불-켜기-Turning-a-light-on" class="headerlink" title="불 켜기, Turning a light on"></a>불 켜기, Turning a light on</h2></li></ol><p><code>api/</code> –&gt;</p>-->]]></content>
      
      
